TI  - Nicotinamide effects oxidative burst activity of neutrophils in patients with poorly controlled type 2 diabetes mellitus
T2  - EXPERIMENTAL DIABESITY RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - NADH
KW  - NADPH oxidase
KW  - neutrophils
KW  - nicotinamide
